== Title? ==

Why does this article bear the ungrammatical title of "France-Asia relations" instead of the proper "Franco-Asian Relations"?  (For non-English speakers, both "France" and "Asia" are nouns but employed here in the place of adjectives, modifying "relations"; the adjectival forms of the two words are "French" and "Asian", but as "French" would stand in first place in a compound adjective, it would be further modified to "Franco-".)  [[User:Firstorm|Firstorm]] ([[User talk:Firstorm|talk]]) 22:21, 15 October 2009 (UTC)
